race.comment: AMRON DANCER (4) recorded a win over 400m at Warragul in an exceptional 22.63 last start. In form and looks the one to beat again. MINTER BLINDER (2) has shown good improvement at his last two starts, breaking through last time at Warragul over 400m. The form out of his last race has been franked. Should feature again. RADIATE (1) produced a modest effort most recently when seventh at Warragul over 400m behind Jumbuk Queen (24.00) in a Mix 6/7. Placed at his previous run. Strong form has emerged from his last run. Will give the top chances plenty to think about. DR. YAMIR (7) cannot be left out after placing last start. Something for the Multiples: GREEN SHOOTS (8)
